 @{b}@{u}Adventure Mania!@{ub}@{uu}

 Adventure Mania! is, according to me anyway, the very first serious Amiga
 adventure solution discazine, containing exactly fifty beautifully written
 walkthroughs.  Indeed, there aren't a lot written by myself, I've searched
 through almost every single Amiga docs disc available on this globe and
 selected the best walkthroughs (the ones without any copyright notice on
 them).  They were all read, corrected when possible and sometimes even part-
 ly rewritten.  But why?  Simply because I've met many people who all had the
 same problem: they were all great adventure fans and were all searching for,
 indeed, walkthroughs.  Now they won't have to search any further, do they?
 Because of 'Adventure Mania!'...    

