one slides down the coal chute! As you look closely, you seem to be looking 
at your twin! Make careful note of the number your "twin" gives you, then 
give him your Spell Book. When you hand him your book, he takes it and makes 
a mad dive down the coal chute leaving you quite alone! No time to waste, 
