east down the coal chute!Your VILSTU potion has about run out and it's doubt-
ful you will survive unless you can get out of here quickly! When you arrive 
back in the Coal Bin Room, standing before you is your younger self! He/You 
is dropping an Orange Vial! Quickly tell your younger self what the combina-
tion to the Dial is! When he gives you the Spell Book, go down the chute and 
outside to.... Fresh air and a Lagoon! As your VILSTU potion wears off, you 
